{
  "texts": [
    "Depending on the use of the replay buffer, current and/or previous samples are provided for the learning step.",
    "Using the updated policy, a new batch of molecules is sampled.",
    "This continues until a stopping criterion has been reached, such as a pre-defined budget of samples.",
    "Molecular de novo design using RNNs for optimizing molecules encoded as SMILES strings, can be formulated as an RL problem.",
    "The agent interacts with the environment over discrete time steps by adding tokens to a SMILES string."
  ]
}